The Galaxy Note series is and always has been about empowering users to do more. The original Note created a new device category, and each subsequent edition has brought tools to help users pursue new passions, unleash their creativity, and be more productive. The Galaxy Note 10 and Note 10+ are the most powerful Notes yet, packed with meaningful improvements in design, performance and more that make it easier for users to bring their ideas to life, and make the most of every moment. Check out the infographic below to explore some of the smartphones’ most exciting new features. For more information, visit Samsung’s website. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-317771" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Infographic_Galaxy-Note10.jpg" alt="Infographic Galaxy Note10" width="640" height="2048" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Infographic_Galaxy-Note10.jpg 1000w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Infographic_Galaxy-Note10-125x400.jpg 125w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Infographic_Galaxy-Note10-768x2458.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Infographic_Galaxy-Note10-134x430.jpg 134w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> This article was published in partnership with Samsung.